name: dying at bass pro shops
description: die at a bass pro shops in northern Indiana. bleed out in front of a group of masturbating idiots. who use fishing and consumerism as methods to euthanize failing marriages and eternal sadness. bite the hook cast from the ceiling. and feel the freedom a big mouth bass feels after finally giving up. submitting to the gutting. to the stupid fucking picture. to the consumption. you don’t need to fight anymore. simply have your lifeless corpse dragged into a boat that will eventually ruin a family.
